reviewText: Older video, looking for something newer, but still learned from it.
lots of good information. but some is mainly for guys with boats and i'm just a poor bank fisher.
Good information on panfish and tactics to catch bigger fish and lots more of them!  Very good layout of DVD!
infisherman staff produce excellent videos that provide not only great footage but also allows the viewer to increase their skill level.
It was nearly as much fun watching this pan fish video as it is catching panfish. Typical of other In-Fisherman video productions.
